228
00:15:03,371 --> 00:15:04,893
Ecco qua.

229
00:15:04,932 --> 00:15:05,092
Com'è?

230
00:15:05,634 --> 00:15:06,193
Bellissimo.

231
00:15:06,453 --> 00:15:07,054
Mi stanno bene?

232
00:15:07,274 --> 00:15:07,956
Benissimo.

233
00:15:07,975 --> 00:15:10,238
Avanti, da bravo.

234
00:15:10,298 --> 00:15:12,980
Che vogliamo tutti sapere come ti chiami.

235
00:15:21,932 --> 00:15:26,614
E quanti anni hai?

236
00:15:26,634 --> 00:15:26,653
90-60.

237
00:15:26,714 --> 00:15:28,673
Oh, così mi piace.

238
00:15:35,115 --> 00:15:35,456
Brucia?

239
00:15:36,255 --> 00:15:37,015
Insopportabile.

240
00:15:41,096 --> 00:15:42,096
È stata fortunata.

241
00:15:43,356 --> 00:15:43,777
Meno male.

242
00:15:44,376 --> 00:15:44,917
Ecco fatto.

243
00:15:45,398 --> 00:15:46,817
Grazie.

244
00:15:46,837 --> 00:15:47,557
Che pensi di fare?

245
00:15:48,216 --> 00:15:51,339
Lo denuncio.

